§7.3 prediction status:
    SPECULATIVE — no obvious 4n² structure jumps out from the binning.
    Binning by 8n-4 (the gap in 4n² triangle numbers) does not reveal
    a striking pattern. Spacing decreases monotonically as expected from
    Riemann-von Mangoldt density growth, with no superimposed 4n² envelope.
    Honest verdict: NOT FALSIFIED but NOT CONFIRMED. §7.3 was flagged
    speculative in the cold derivation; this result keeps it flagged speculative.
    A positive identification would require a more principled binning rule
    derived directly from RS2-105 (quantum π = 4) rather than ad-hoc.
